Subject:Re: [Jukebox-list] Vinyl record
A diamond or carbide grit hole saw will minimize the risk. Use water with 
it. You may have to retrofit the pilot drill bit with a smooth pilot of the 
appropriate diameter. This setup, especially in a drill press, should not be 
much of a risk.

Danno
